@startuml andersonkmi_credit-card-bindb-service-aws

actor "External User" as User
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "Lambda (CSV Reader)" as LambdaReader
participant "S3" as S3
queue "SQS" as SQS
participant "Lambda (Processor)" as LambdaProcessor
database "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB

User -> APIGateway : Request BIN data
APIGateway -> LambdaReader : Trigger CSV reading
LambdaReader -> S3 : Read CSV file
S3 --> LambdaReader : Return CSV data
LambdaReader -> SQS : Split and send messages
SQS --> LambdaProcessor : Trigger processing
LambdaProcessor -> DynamoDB : Store processed BIN data
DynamoDB --> LambdaProcessor : Confirm storage
LambdaProcessor --> APIGateway : Return response
APIGateway --> User : Deliver BIN data

@enduml